= Locations =

'''Dragon Quest III''' (SNES) features a vast world map based on the real world, with locations spanning multiple continents.

__TOC__

== World Overview ==

The game world is divided into:
* '''Upper World''' - Main world based on real Earth geography
* '''Alefgard''' - Underground world (connects to DQ1)
* '''Dark World''' - Baramos and Zoma's domains

